{"tid":969611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美極右派「熱舞影片」修理民主黨超紅女議員　網力挺：戀愛了","createTime":"2019-01-05T07:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T08:08:39.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f2338c6c16529b91a16b912ec17d51fd6d2bffc8","tid":969611,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3812/d3812475.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3812%2Fd3812475.jpg&h=05e73cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲奧卡西歐(Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez)熱舞影片曝光。（圖／路透）<br />\n實習記者鄭佩玟／綜合報導<br />\n美國第116屆國會的超級新星，剛滿29歲的紐約州聯邦眾議員奧卡西歐‧寇特茲，在新國會開議的這一天，因右翼人士公開她少女時期熱舞影片，再度成為話題焦點，原來要詆毀的意圖更瞬間被網友翻盤，紛紛相挺「很可愛」、「戀愛了」。奧卡西歐4日也上傳自己跳舞的影片，拍攝地點就是自家辦公室，霸氣回應「聽說共和黨認為女性跳舞是可恥的喔。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3812/d3812476.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3812%2Fd3812476.jpg&h=8b683b51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美國民主黨籍的紐約州新科聯邦眾議員奧卡西歐─寇特茲是政壇新星(Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez)。（圖／路透）<br />\n據《今日美國》報導，持左派立場的奧卡西歐（Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez）為本屆最年輕的議員，直到2018年2月都還在紐約付近一家西班牙餐廳吧台調酒，參與黨內初選時，媒體連她的名字都不願放進標題，讓她自嘲是「沒有名字的女孩」，沒想到驚奇之旅才剛開始，一舉扳倒勇有近20年資歷的聯邦眾議員克勞利（Joseph Crowley），成功獲得民主黨提名後，當選聯邦眾議員。<br />\n在卡西歐3日在眾議院宣誓就職後，當晚推特（Twitter）上一名右派陰謀論用戶「@AnonymousQ1776」公開一段31秒的影片，指出這是奧卡西歐高中時期的影片，內容是她在建築物屋頂歡樂跳舞，用戶還開嘲諷，「這就是美國最受喜歡的知性共產黨分子，行為像個一無所知的低能兒。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3812/d3812474.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3812%2Fd3812474.jpg&h=c94d3c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲奧卡西歐2011年從波士頓大學畢業，獲得經濟學與國際關係雙學位。（圖／路透）<br />\n事實上，這則影片是早就被剪輯過，原影片長達4分20秒，8年前就在YouTube公開過，由波士頓大學（Boston University）學生拍攝的「復古青春校園混剪影片」（Brat Pack Mashup），背景音樂還是法國復古搖滾樂團「鳳凰樂團」（Phoenix）的經典單曲「李斯特狂熱」（Lisztomania），這首歌大量被美國知名電影及電視影集所使用，紅極一時。<br />\n當時全世界都流行以「李斯特狂熱」為背景音樂，拍攝模仿1980年代青春電影風格的影片。波士頓大學也跟上這股風潮，奧卡西歐則是被找來的其中一名舞者，他們以1985年美國青春喜劇電影《早餐俱樂部》（The Breakfast Club）內的一段舞蹈，混搭「李斯特狂熱」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FI5yvdaMIPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFI5yvdaMIPU&d=6LjHaz1FPxgum3j4BAfkLMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=fe935090\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FI5yvdaMIPU</a><br />\n事與願違，極右派陰謀者的下作手段恐怕完全沒用，因推特上大部分網友都力挺奧卡西歐，「太可愛了吧」、「我更愛她了！」抹黑影片迅速爆紅，面對眾人的無情圍剿，讓發布者無地自容，幾小時後就刪除自己的帳號，日前在推特上「查無此人」<br />\n奧卡西歐更親自錄下一段11秒的影片回擊，搭配愛德溫&bull;史塔爾（Edwin Starr）的反戰名曲「戰爭」（War）作為背景音樂，向鏡頭對嘴唱，「這有好處嗎？什麼都沒有。」俏皮地小秀一段舞蹈後，開門進入辦公室。這段影片4日下午上傳至今已突破千萬人次觀看。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190105/1348750.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190105%2F1348750.htm&d=6LjHaz1FPxgum3j4BAfkLMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=10a7e02b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190105/1348750.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.vanityfair.com/photos/5b36544dbcde924f1fa9b5a8/master/pass/Alexandria-Ocasio-Cortex-documentarian.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.vanityfair.com%2Fphotos%2F5b36544dbcde924f1fa9b5a8%2Fmaster%2Fpass%2FAlexandria-Ocasio-Cortex-documentarian.jpg&h=991f79a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.townhall.com/townhall/reu/ha/2018/221/d9998677-14fc-4f2f-b26b-f53b23a2a4e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.townhall.com%2Ftownhall%2Freu%2Fha%2F2018%2F221%2Fd9998677-14fc-4f2f-b26b-f53b23a2a4e6.jpg&h=642ab3ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10a67a93ae3e4df7b9de705cfe744b4fff3206d7","tid":969611,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a22a4fc5e2527cae8fb2b8cd268832872892520","tid":969611,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://media.townhall.com/townhall/reu/ha/2018/221/d9998677-14fc-4f2f-b26b-f53b23a2a4e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.townhall.com%2Ftownhall%2Freu%2Fha%2F2018%2F221%2Fd9998677-14fc-4f2f-b26b-f53b23a2a4e6.jpg&h=72a7cee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/da9/098/da9098bc6fae5d09320194727e4cc9a9a344685f_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fda9%2F098%2Fda9098bc6fae5d09320194727e4cc9a9a344685f_n.jpg&h=45d3866c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b51457d526fa983960f11437632a0ab20d2c253a","tid":969611,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:48:20.000Z","msg":"好彩冇除褲"},{"pid":"3859231c84ccff970ca49ece2c59e40c10021de4","tid":969611,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"蒙頭入閘"},{"pid":"fe19d5c4a09549c45ba9cd6e6654f236b4e7e6fd","tid":969611,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:49:43.000Z","msg":"事實證明．．．西方佬真係好鐘意有色皮膚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a316bfe76d19f87b873287e6489e18bde5f338a","tid":969611,"uid":73613,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0e70b210079827a44a60852e59d49b0676cb905","tid":969611,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T07:52:57.000Z","msg":"又咪俾白鬼當Mary咁屌口"},{"pid":"d37124277fe9533e64f033570e7349ad185a1bec","tid":969611,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:08:39.000Z","msg":"好樣衰"}]}